OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,FA man believed to be the UK's longest
OL,7,Fserving bus driver has vowed to stay
OL,8,Fbehind the wheel.
OL,10,FKenny Beckers, 76, from Swansea, has
OL,11,Fdriven buses since he was 21.
OL,13,FMr Beckers' employer, First Bus,
OL,14,Festimated he has driven seven million
OL,15,Fcustomers and clocked up around
OL,16,F800,000 miles in his five decades as a
OL,17,Fbus driver.
OL,19,FThere is no maximum age for someone to
OL,20,Fbe a bus driver in the UK.
