OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,FThe grandfather began his career as a
OL,7,Fconductor at the age of 18, before
OL,8,Fbecoming a driver three years later.
OL,10,FHe has worked for five different
OL,11,Fcompanies in his tenure and has always
OL,12,Fbeen based in Swansea.
OL,14,FMr Becker said: "It was great being a
OL,15,Fdriver in 1969. We had so many routes
OL,16,Fand carried so many passengers,
OL,17,Fincluding lots from all the factories,
OL,18,Fthe collieries and British Steel at
OL,19,FPort Talbot, but, of course, all that
OL,20,Fdeclined in the 1980s.
