OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,F"I also remember we had double-deckers
OL,7,Fback then, but passengers were only
OL,8,Fallowed to smoke on the top deck.
OL,10,F"Upstairs was like a mist. All the
OL,11,Ffactory girls and everybody else was
OL,12,Fup there smoking, it was unbelievable."
OL,14,FMr Beckers said the "loss of
OL,15,Fcommuters" has been the biggest change
OL,16,Fduring his career.
OL,18,FHe said: "The reduction in office
OL,19,Fworkers and shop workers, and more
OL,20,Fpeople buying cars, means we've seen a
OL,21,Fdecline in bus travel.
