OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,F"However, we are doing a lot more for
OL,7,Fdisabled people now. Back in the day,
OL,8,Fbuses had steps so if you had a pram
OL,9,For a buggy you just had to fold it up
OL,10,Fand get on with it.
OL,12,F"We now have buses that are lower,
OL,13,Fpavements that are higher and ramps.
OL,15,F"It's great to see services increasing
OL,16,Fagain in Swansea, as the key to
OL,17,Fgetting people back on the bus is by
OL,18,Fputting on more services, but I
OL,19,Fcompletely understand that it's a fine
OL,20,Fline.
