OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,F"But things are definitely picking up
OL,7,Fand that's great news."
OL,9,FMr Beckers is in semi-retirement
OL,10,Fworking two days a week, but has no
OL,11,Fintention of stopping completely.
OL,13,FHe said: "Once my body feels like
OL,14,Fenough is enough then I'll give up,
OL,15,Fbut I don't like putting a time on
OL,16,Fthings.
OL,18,F"I've seen people put times on stuff,
OL,19,Fand then everything goes haywire for a
OL,20,Ftime. I don't want to put a date on it.
