OL,3,CUK's longest serving bus driver, 76,
OL,4,Cvows to 'keep going' behind the wheel
OL,6,F"In all my years working I've never
OL,7,Freally thought about giving up the
OL,8,Fjob, and I can honestly say I've never
OL,9,Fhad that moment of 'I've had enough,
OL,10,FI'm off'.
OL,12,F"So long as I feel good and my
OL,13,Fhealth's good, then I'll keep going."
